Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.85,0:00:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是想要我从银河里最聪明的哺乳动物那儿套情报\N{\fs38}You want me to get intel out of the smartest mammal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们最好给我配台先进的析脑仪"\N{\fs38}in the galaxy, you’d better give me a decent brainalyzer.”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.73,0:00:54.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是也点几个煎饼\N{\fs38}Well, you might as well order some pancakes,
