Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.75,0:01:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进展怎么样\N{\fs38}What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.48,0:01:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚不明朗 他好像臆想出了某种屁股\N{\fs38}It’s hard to tell.He may have manifested some sort of butt.
