Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是宇宙里最聪明的人\N{\fs38}He is the smartest man in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你们讲 银河联邦接管地球\N{\fs38}I tell you, the Galactic Federation taking over Earth --
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我们家遇到过最好的事\N{\fs38}best thing that’s ever happened to this family.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个星期我刚被提拔了第六次\N{\fs38}I just got my sixth promotion this week,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我都还不知道上班是干嘛\N{\fs38}and I still don’t know what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁在乎你被提拔得多高啊\N{\fs38}Who cares how high they promote you?
