Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.93,0:02:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你自己靠不知道干什么挣钱了\N{\fs38}Well, when you’re not sure what you do for a living,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.89,0:02:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干什么都随你\N{\fs38}you can make your own rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.35,0:02:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Summer 对你爸爸尊敬点儿\N{\fs38}Summer, show your father some respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:17.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他挣的可是六"味"数的收入呢\N{\fs38}He’s pulling down a six-chewable-figure income.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待会儿我来收拾 大家的药丸味道怎么样\N{\fs38}-[ Glass shatters] -I’ll get that in a moment.How are everyone’s pills?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 Morty 你都没怎么吃你的药丸啊\N{\fs38}Oh, Morty, you’ve hardly touched your pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午餐药丸吃的有点儿多 而且我\N{\fs38}I kind of had big pills for lunch, and I...
