Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我谢你啊 Conroy\N{\fs38}Thank you, Conroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会宠坏我们的 Conroy\N{\fs38}You spoil us, Conroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这要是外公绝对忍不了\N{\fs38}Grandpa Rick wouldn’t put up with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别提他的名字 他抛弃了我们\N{\fs38}STop saying his name. He abandoned us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.29,0:02:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是Willem Dafoe!\N{\fs38}Willem Dafoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我今早想不起名字的就是这个人\N{\fs38}T-That’s the guy I couldn’t think of this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别重蹈我的覆辙 Summer\N{\fs38}Don’t make my mistake, Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别神化弃你而去的人\N{\fs38}Don’t deify the people that leave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的下场就是个马外科医生 活在外星人统治的世界\N{\fs38}You’ll end up a horse surgeon in a world controlled by aliens
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而外星药物会让马儿们 永葆健康\N{\fs38}whose medicine keeps horses... healthy forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在马比王八命还长\N{\fs38}Horses live longer than tortoises now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要沦落于此吗\N{\fs38}Is that what you want for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我要的只是在我大叫着跑掉的时候你还会在乎\N{\fs38}Maybe I just want you to care if I run away yelling!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁要来些药丸布蕾\N{\fs38}Who saved room for pill brülée?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.73,0:03:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能理解你为什么选了这间家庭餐厅\N{\fs38}I can see why you chose this family-friendly restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来显现你的小脑\N{\fs38}to represent your cerebellum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给人安全感 又舒适温馨 很有肖尼斯的感觉\N{\fs38}So safe, so comfortable, so Shoney’s.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.82,0:03:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是承认吧 Rick 一直待在这儿你会疯掉的\N{\fs38}But admit it, Rick -- You’re going crazy cooped up in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去别的记忆里头逛逛吧\N{\fs38}Let’s go visit some memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 想看特定的哪一个吗\N{\fs38}Oh, any particular ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想看我第一次勃起吗\N{\fs38}You want to see my first boner
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是要直接去看\N{\fs38}or should we go straight to the moment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发现次元穿越方法的那一刻\N{\fs38}I discovered interdimensional travel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那下垂的两根在抽呢\N{\fs38}Ooh. Your little flappy doodles are twitching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是性奋了\N{\fs38}Does that mean you’re aroused,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是你收到信号 有同伴找到了一串葡萄\N{\fs38}or did you just get a signal that one of your buddies found a grape?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是兴奋\N{\fs38}It’s arousal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我很乐意去看看\N{\fs38}Yes, I’d like very much to visit the memory
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你发明传送门枪的那段记忆\N{\fs38}of you inventing your portal gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我的山芋很烫手啊\N{\fs38}-Yeah. Well, tough titties. -[ Rumbling, glass breaking ]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有比神经崩溃更烫手的山芋吗 Rick\N{\fs38}There’s no tougher titty than a psychotic break, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.43,0:03:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 那就要看是什么先崩溃了 我 还是 山芋\N{\fs38}Well, that depends on who breaks first -- me or the titty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是某个你记忆里特别的人吗\N{\fs38}Someone special you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对她的记忆就放在这儿吗\N{\fs38}Is that your memory of her out there --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.19,0:03:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,排在911惊魂未定和最爱的体育糗事之间\N{\fs38}between where you were on 9/11 and your favorite sports blooper?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们呆在这儿 你会死的 同所有的记忆一起死去\N{\fs38}If we stay here, you’ll die, along with all your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你带我去我想去的地方\N{\fs38}If you take me where I want to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也会在那儿 对吗\N{\fs38}she’ll be there, too, won’t she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发明传送门枪的那天就是我失去她的那天\N{\fs38}The day I invented the portal gun is the day I lost her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:03:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来不错啊\N{\fs38}Oh, that sounds cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.04,0:04:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能弄到我想要的 你也能道个别\N{\fs38}I can get what I want and you can say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 但是我来开车\N{\fs38}[Sighs] Fine, but I’m driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为剥去我们自由的借口\N{\fs38}.as an excuse to strip away our freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是 你这是在干嘛\N{\fs38}Huh? What are you -- What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外公肯定有秘密实验室 对吧\N{\fs38}Grandpa Rick must have some secret lab, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏着镭射枪 喷气背包 还有太空坦克\N{\fs38}With, like, laser guns and jets packs and a space tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我们可以去劫他出狱\N{\fs38}And we can go break him out of prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看这些死苍蝇\N{\fs38}Look at these dead flies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定按照一定的顺序排列\N{\fs38}Maybe if we arrange them in a certain order,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会放一段全息图 或者打开一扇暗门\N{\fs38}it plays a hologram or it opens a secret door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Summer 你吓着我了\N{\fs38}Summer, you’re freaking me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道世界变了样 也知道你想念Rick了\N{\fs38}I know things have changed a lot, and I know you miss Rick,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是把他弄回来也不会有所好转\N{\fs38}but getting him back wouldn’t make things better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我们过得也不算糟糕\N{\fs38}And, you know, we’re not doing so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过得糟糕透了 Morty\N{\fs38}We’re miserable, Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅强制宵禁 按他们奇怪的历法算起来我有47岁\N{\fs38}There’s a mandatory curfew, their weird calendar made me 47,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃菲尔铁塔被变成了武器\N{\fs38}and they weapon ized the Eiffel Tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得35岁挺好 我 我现在都可以租车了\N{\fs38}I like being 35. I-I can rent a car now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你就是个烂人\N{\fs38}Because you suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外公被捕之后你就一言不发\N{\fs38}You’ve been keeping your lip zipped about it since Grandpa got arrested,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.44,0:04:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甩掉了他你其实爽得不行\N{\fs38}but the fact is,you’re freaking stoked to bail on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他甩掉了所有人\N{\fs38}He bails on everybody!
