Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我以前没说清楚 Summer\N{\fs38}And in case I never made this clear to you, Summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也甩掉了你\N{\fs38}he bailed on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把你撇在一个被他毁了的世界里自生自灭\N{\fs38}He left you to rot in a world that he ruined
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:04:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他不在乎\N{\fs38}because he doesn’t care!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他不在乎任何人 Summer\N{\fs38}Because nobody’s special to him, Summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:04:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连他自己也不在乎\N{\fs38}not even himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你要是真想找回你的外公 拿把铁锹\N{\fs38}So if you really want your grandpa back, grab a shovel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你失望的那个外公 就埋在你家后院里\N{\fs38}The one that won’t let you down is buried in your backyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说对了\N{\fs38}You’re right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 不是 我才没说对\N{\fs38}What?! No! I’m not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说气话激你而已\N{\fs38}I-I was using ghoulish overkill!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是气话 Summer\N{\fs38}Ghoulish overkill, Summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐 天呐\N{\fs38}Oh, God! Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这是去哪儿\N{\fs38}Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去所有一切开始的那天 也是终结的那天\N{\fs38}To the day it all began and ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有事情转折的那一刻\N{\fs38}The moment that changed everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到麦当劳 请问您想点些什么\N{\fs38}MAN: Welcome to McDonald’s. Can I take your order?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要十块麦乐鸡 多给点川香酱\N{\fs38}Yeah, I’d like to get a 10-piece McNugget and, uh, a bunch of the Szechuan sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能给多少酱就给多少酱\N{\fs38}Like, as much as you’re allowed to give me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在1998年 麦当劳给迪士尼电影<花木兰>做宣传\N{\fs38}In 1998, they had this promotion for the Disney film “Mulan,”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时他们 当时他们\N{\fs38}where they -- where they --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们给麦乐鸡配制了一种新的蘸酱\N{\fs38}they created a new sauce for the McNuggets
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做川香酱 超级好吃\N{\fs38}called Szechuan sauce, and it’s delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来他们就取消了 现在都没了\N{\fs38}And then they got rid of it, and now it’s gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.23,0:05:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有在记忆里能让我们尝到了\N{\fs38}The only place we’re gonna be able to try it is in my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 你做这件事的同时你的大脑在融化\N{\fs38}Rick, you’re doing this bit while your brain is melting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 好的 好的\N{\fs38}Okay. All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那个是 - 我\N{\fs38}Is that...Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:05:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前穿蓝色裤子\N{\fs38}I used to wear blue pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么时候实现跨次元旅行的\N{\fs38}When’d you make the leap to interdimensional travel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有 是我做的\N{\fs38}I didn’t. I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 哦 哦 这不是我们嘛\N{\fs38}Well, well, well. If it isn’t us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.38,0:06:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道发明传送技术最糟糕的一点是什么吗\N{\fs38}You know the worst part about inventing teleportation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然间 你能够穿梭于整个银河\N{\fs38}Suddenly you’re able to travel the whole galaxy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你发现的第一件事情就是\N{\fs38}and the first thing you learn is
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是最后一个发明了传输技术的人\N{\fs38}you’re the last guy to invent teleportation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸运的是 你将发明一件更加厉害的东西\N{\fs38}Fortunately, you’re about to invent something much more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs38}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Summer 这事儿没必要让别人知道\N{\fs38}Summer, nobody has to know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以把它放回去 然后假装从来没看见过\N{\fs38}We could put it right back and pretend we never saw it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我们也没见过老爸的塑料假人大腿一样\N{\fs38}like we did with Dad’s mannequin leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 你留在这儿 我自己去救外公\N{\fs38}Fine. Stay here. I’ll rescue Grandpa myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你要怎么做 - 我还不知道\N{\fs38}-How are you gonna do that?! -l don’t know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船到桥头自然直 外公不就是这样吗\N{\fs38}I’ll make it up as I go. That’s what Grandpa Rick does.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄不就是这样吗\N{\fs38}That’s what heroes do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你想要看Rick是什么样的英雄吗\N{\fs38}You want to see what a hero Rick is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我带你去个地方 Summer\N{\fs38}I-Ill bring you somewhere, Summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 嗯 - 我的天呐 孩子们\N{\fs38}-Urn... -My goodness, children.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下那个非法科技\N{\fs38}[Sternly] Relinquish the illegal technology
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给最近的联邦议员\N{\fs38}to the nearest Federation representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我们来玩"胡言乱语"猜谜游戏\N{\fs38}[Normal voice ] And then we’ll all play Balderdash.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我的天呐\N{\fs38}[Grunts] Oh, my goodness!Oh! Oh! My goo-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我的天呀\N{\fs38}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.45,0:07:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一件一模一样的上衣\N{\fs38}I have that exact same Top.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是哪里\N{\fs38}What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.33,0:07:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这个<饥饿游戏>版的Summer是怎么回事\N{\fs38}And what’s with “Hunger Games” Summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的姐姐 这里原来是我的家\N{\fs38}That’s my sister. This used to be my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想看 任何事情你都能做到\N{\fs38}Imagine doing anything you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳到一个你从未到过的时间线\N{\fs38}then hopping to a timeline where you never did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去任何地点 任何时间 没人能拦住你\N{\fs38}Imagine going anywhere, anytime, with nobody able to sTop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来挺孤单的\N{\fs38}Sounds lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤单 老兄 你有你自己\N{\fs38}Lonely?Dude, you have yourself --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无数个你自己\N{\fs38}your infinite selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一场永不散场的聚会\N{\fs38}It’s a nonsTop party
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的来宾都是我们唯一喜欢的那个人\N{\fs38}where all the guests are the only person we like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为做地球上最聪明的人是一件很酷的事情\N{\fs38}You think it’s cool being the smartest man on Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一旦我们给你这项技术\N{\fs38}but once we give you this technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就变成每个可构想的世界里最聪明的人了\N{\fs38}you become the smartest thing in every conceivable universe --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无限的Rick 一个神\N{\fs38}the Infinite Rick, a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了吧\N{\fs38}Enh, pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 老兄 Rick们不会就这样算了的\N{\fs38}Excuse me? Bro, Ricks don’t pass on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.53,0:07:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为你是谁\N{\fs38}Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,—个不一样的Rick 我猜\N{\fs38}A different kind of Rick, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我们来看看这能持续多久\N{\fs38}Well, we’ll see how long that lasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到了挺科幻的声音\N{\fs38}I heard sci-fi noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有了进展吗\N{\fs38}Did you make a breakthrough?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点吧\N{\fs38}Sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我仔细地看了看自己\N{\fs38}I just took a long look at myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想科学这条路或许走不通\N{\fs38}and I don’t think this science thing is gonna pay off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 为什么不带上Beth 然后一起出去吃冰淇淋呢\N{\fs38}Well, why don’t I get Beth and we’ll go out for ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dianne 那是在这间车库里面\N{\fs38}That, Diane, is the last great idea
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.26,0:08:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会诞生的最后一个好主意了\N{\fs38}that will ever be had in this garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这柯南伯格怪烤得挺好的\N{\fs38}Good roasted Cronenberg, I assume.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 你看起来 很野性\N{\fs38}Mom, you’re looking...feral.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢相信Rick居然做了这种事情\N{\fs38}I can’t believe Rick did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick的冒险里的这一部分\N{\fs38}These are the parts of Rick’s adventures
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你见不到的 他抛下不管的那部分\N{\fs38}you don’t get to see -- the parts he leaves behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 谢谢款待\N{\fs38}All right. IVs been great, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是来跑一趟 实地展示下"我就跟你说吧"\N{\fs38}Urn, I really only wanted to sTop by here for a quick “I told you so.”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 所以 嗯 - 在找这个吗\N{\fs38}-So, uh... -Looking for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拿着这个要干嘛\N{\fs38}What are you doing with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它有Rick的臭味\N{\fs38}It stinks of Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 为什么 为什么你要这么做\N{\fs38}[ Grunts] -No! Why?!Why would you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你 你们这些人有什么毛病\N{\fs38}W-What is the matter with you people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这帮野蛮人 原始的野蛮傻逼\N{\fs38}You’re a bunch of back savages --backwood savage morons!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你永远不能离开 她不能留下\N{\fs38}You can never leave. She cannot remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她有Rick的臭味\N{\fs38}She stinks of Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.89,0:09:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开枪 别开枪\N{\fs38}Hold your fire! Hold your fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是Morty C-137\N{\fs38}I’m Morty 0-137.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们探测到一个被毁坏的传输枪 你的Rick哪去了\N{\fs38}We detected a compromised portal gun.Where is your Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他被捕了 - Summer\N{\fs38}-He’s in prison. - Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他被银河联邦抓住了\N{\fs38}He got captured by the Federation,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们打算去救他\N{\fs38}and we were going to rescue him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是令人烦恼 我们不能让大本营的秘密\N{\fs38}Very troubling.We can’t risk Citadel secrets
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯险落入银河联邦的手中\N{\fs38}falling into the Federation’s hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们马上派Rick海豹突击队\N{\fs38}We’ll dispatch S.E.A.L. Team Ricks immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闯入关押C-137的监狱\N{\fs38}to break into the prison holding 0-137...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 超帅 - 然后刺杀他\N{\fs38}Boo-yah....and assassinate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超衰\N{\fs38}Boo-nah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 姑娘们 冰淇淋要化掉了\N{\fs38}-[ Horn honks] -Come on, girls!The ice cream’s gonna melt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs38}N o-o-o-o-o-o-o!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哦 这酱真他妈好吃\N{\fs38}Wow. This sauce is tucking amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了宣传一部电影是吗\N{\fs38}You said it was promoting a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把3移项 再加2\N{\fs38}Carry the 3, add a 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.61,0:10:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成了 他妈的成了\N{\fs38}I got it.I tucking got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哦 就 就是这个吗 传送枪\N{\fs38}Whoa. I-Is that it -- the portal gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 就是那三行公式\N{\fs38}Yeah.That’s the three lines of math
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分隔了我的人生\N{\fs38}that separates my life as a man
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.47,0:10:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一边是生活中的人 一边是无知无觉的鬼魂\N{\fs38}from my life as an unfeeling ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒棒的\N{\fs38}Awesome possum.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制中心 你们拿到这个了吗\N{\fs38}Mission Control, you getting this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐 是的 是的 我们拿到了 是的\N{\fs38}Holy shit, yes!Yes! We got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 Rick 我会试着记住关掉析脑仪的\N{\fs38}Yeah! All right! Thanks, Rick.I’ll try to remember to shut off the brainalyzer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实 我想它会自动关闭的\N{\fs38}Actually, I think it shuts off automatically
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你的大脑液化以后\N{\fs38}once your brain is liquid.
