Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安保事故\N{\fs38}Security breach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一座全是外公的城市吗\N{\fs38}A city of Grandpas?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是Rick的大本营\N{\fs38}It's the Citadel of Ricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有来自不同时空的不同Rick\N{\fs38}All the different Ricks from all the different realities
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起聚在这里躲避政府\N{\fs38}got together to hide here from the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果政府每个Rick都痛恨政府\N{\fs38}But if every Rick hates the government,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么他们还会恨我们的外公\N{\fs38}why would they hate Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为Rick最痛恨的是他们自己\N{\fs38}Because Ricks hate themselves the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们的Rick最是他自己\N{\fs38}And our Rick is the most... himself.
