Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.15,0:12:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick海豹突击队把他的一字眉\N{\fs38}S.E.A.L. Team Ricks turned his unibrow
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分成了两根眉毛 用子弹分的\N{\fs38}into two brows -- with a bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的Rick死了 你们的Rick死了\N{\fs38}Your Rick’s dead! Your Rick’s dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:12:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官 Rick D-99 正单独返回\N{\fs38}Sir, Rick D-99 is returning from the mission alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很显然 Rick海豹突击队损失惨重\N{\fs38}Apparently, S.E.A.L. Team Ricks suffered heavy casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他进来\N{\fs38}Bring him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他只愿意与一名更高级别的Rick通话\N{\fs38}He says he’ll only talk to a Rick with higher clearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矫情 把那玩意儿给我\N{\fs38}La-d i-da. Give me that.
