Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个间谍 炸了他 我要去拉屎\N{\fs38}He’s a spy. Blow him up. I’m gonna go take a shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操作一支未注册的传送枪\N{\fs38}Operating an unregistered portal gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将一名Summer转变为激进分子\N{\fs38}radicalizing a Summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且与一个叛徒Rick合谋\N{\fs38}conspiring with a traitorous Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对此你如何辩护\N{\fs38}How do you plead?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.56,0:13:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么算得上是个公平的审判啊\N{\fs38}How is this a fair trial?
