Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty\N{\fs38}Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs38}-[ Whispers indistinctly] -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我才不要看你的游戏币收藏\N{\fs38}N-No, I don’t want to see your pog collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有与Rick断绝关系 我从来都没有\N{\fs38}I don’t renounce Rick, and I never have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.01,0:13:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想保护我的姐姐\N{\fs38}I was just trying to protect my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让你有正常的生活\N{\fs38}I wanted you to have a normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是每次Rick出现时你就无法拥有的生活\N{\fs38}That’s something you can’t have when Rick shows up.
