Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别他妈这么深情地缅怀他\N{\fs38}Let’s not suck the ghost of his dick too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:20.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个恐怖分子 现在他死了\N{\fs38}He was a terrorist, and now he’s dead.
