Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大本营被传送到了联邦的地盘\N{\fs38}The Citadel has been teleported to [burps] Federation space.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完蛋了 这一定是C-137干的\N{\fs38}It’s doomed. This has to be C-137, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.43,0:15:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们该怎么办 - 他要找我们算账了\N{\fs38}-What are we gonna do?! -You know he’s coming for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.89,0:15:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 都冷静 我们可以把他的Summer当做人质\N{\fs38}All right! Calm down! We have his Summer as a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.14,0:15:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很显然 我抓住她了\N{\fs38}Obviously, I get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们用"瑞克 激光 剪刀"决定谁抓住Morty\N{\fs38}You guys play Rick, Laser, Scissors for the Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是出的什么\N{\fs38}W-What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报复\N{\fs38}Payback.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外公\N{\fs38}Grandpa Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 还用说吗 - 你还活着\N{\fs38}-Duh. -You’re alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Rick - Morty 拿着这个 待会儿用得上\N{\fs38}-Rick! -Morty, take this.You’re gonna need it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 等等 喔\N{\fs38}Hold on. Hold on. Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 Rick\N{\fs38}COUNCIL MEMBER: That’s enough, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是想干什么\N{\fs38}What -- What’s this supposed to accomplish?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的外孙多得用不完\N{\fs38}We have infinite grandkids.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这好比是想在凯撒宫酒店里花掉迪士尼代币\N{\fs38}You’re trying to use Disney bucks at a Caesars Palace here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:15:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在唬你 他很爱我的\N{\fs38}[Gasps ] That’s a bluff. He’s bluffing, sir. He loves me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不按套路出牌 不理性又感情用事\N{\fs38}You’re a rogue Rick -- irrational, passionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爱你的外孙 你来这儿就是要救他们\N{\fs38}You love your grandkids. You came to rescue them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来杀你的 哥们\N{\fs38}I came to kill you, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都不是我原装的Summer\N{\fs38}That’s not even my original Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈呀 他不是在唬人\N{\fs38}Oh, my God. He’s not bluffing. He’s not bluffing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Rick - 干嘛不直接射穿她\N{\fs38}-R-Rick? -Why not shoot through her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20码的距离 9口径脉冲手枪\N{\fs38}Twenty yards, nine-gauge plasma pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的第一枪会液化她的内脏 但只能打伤你\N{\fs38}My first shot would liquify her insides and injure you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二枪后坐力会增加\N{\fs38}second shot adds recoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我等你枪毙她 我的风险就会降到最低\N{\fs38}The risk to me is minimized if I wait for you to shoot her,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就希望你这么做\N{\fs38}which I’m encouraging you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 搞什么啊 - 或者放了她\N{\fs38}-What the fuck?! -Or let her go,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我就可以让你死得痛快些\N{\fs38}which I will reward with a quicker death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你爱她\N{\fs38}Because you love her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你才能让我给你最利索的一枪\N{\fs38}Because it’s incentive for you to give me my cleanest shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死得不那么痛苦\N{\fs38}which will be your least painful death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果你想要死得慢些 我也很有兴趣陪你玩\N{\fs38}But if you want to die slower than that, I’m super into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想这么做的话你只需要杀了那个女孩\N{\fs38}All you got to do to get that started is kill the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我恨你 - 我才不在乎 亲爱的\N{\fs38}-I hate you! -Not an issue, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:40.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 把枪放下 Rick\N{\fs38}That’s enough! Drop the gun, Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.30,0:16:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 我知道你太蠢了 不懂我在干嘛\N{\fs38}Morty, I know you’re too stupid to get this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你现在真他妈是在捣乱\N{\fs38}but you’re really fucking this up right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能让你害死我姐姐 把枪放下\N{\fs38}I’m not letting you let my sister die!Drop the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没想让她死 你这傻逼\N{\fs38}I wasn’t gonna let her die, you fucking moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 哈 - 噢\N{\fs38}-Ha! -Aww.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关键是让他以为我打算这么做\N{\fs38}The point is he thought I was going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便说一句 我确实被你骗到了\N{\fs38}I totally did, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真傻逼 Morty\N{\fs38}You’re a fucking moron, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 你这智障\N{\fs38}Morty, you fucking idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真他妈的是个智障 Morty\N{\fs38}You’re a serious fucking idiot, Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这等于是害死了我们所有人\N{\fs38}You basically killed us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:16:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你太烂了 - 你傻得和一袋沙子没啥区别\N{\fs38}-You’re the worst! -You’re dumb as a bag of sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看现在到底是谁傻\N{\fs38}Who’s stupid now, bitch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 他才刚回到我们身边\N{\fs38}Morty! We just got him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得漂亮啊 Morty\N{\fs38}[Laughs I That was amazing, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天啊 你可真棒\N{\fs38}Oh, my God. Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 现在我们来做个了结\N{\fs38}Okay. Let’s wrap this --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 Morty 我们走吧 孩子们\N{\fs38}Good job, Morty. Let’s go, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥 刚才是怎么回事\N{\fs38}What?! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是我的老把戏罢了\N{\fs38}Oldest Rick trick in the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"枪是假的 僵持时朝我开枪"\N{\fs38}“Fake gun. Shoot me in standoff.”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 太机智啦 - 哈 没错\N{\fs38}—Brilliant! -Ha! Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.01,0:17:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好我看见字条了\N{\fs38}G-Good thing I saw that note.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就不能直接传送回家吗\N{\fs38}Couldn’t we just portal home?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.35,0:17:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我收拾好我搞出来的烂摊子再说\N{\fs38}Not until I finish what I started.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是不用密码就能获得九级权限的办法\N{\fs38}And that is how you get Ievel-9 access without a password.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.11,0:17:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动\N{\fs38}Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.11,0:17:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家请看 月度最佳员工\N{\fs38}Employee of the month, ladies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你到底要用九级权限做什么\N{\fs38}So what are you doing with level-9 access anyways?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.49,0:17:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 毁掉银河联邦啊 - 棒极了 - 哇 太酷了\N{\fs38}- Destroying the [burps] Galactic government.-Awesome! -Whoa! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是要让他们用核武器自相残杀吗\N{\fs38}Are you going to set all their nukes to target each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:54.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 还可以重新设定他们军队的传送门\N{\fs38}Ooh, or -- or reprogram their military portals
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来毁掉他们所有的太空舰队\N{\fs38}to disintegrate their entire space fleet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意 孩子们 快要为你们骄傲了\N{\fs38}Good pitches, kids. I’m almost proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:18:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你们看仔细点 外公马上要摧毁一个帝国了\N{\fs38}But watch closely as Grandpa Topples an empire
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把这个1改成0\N{\fs38}by changing a one...to a zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生 咱们货币刚刚跌到一文不值了\N{\fs38}Mr. President, the Blemflarck’s value just dropped to nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fs38}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.97,0:18:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说 银河联邦的唯一货币\N{\fs38}I mean our single centralized Galactic currency
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚还一块钱值一块钱 现在一块钱的价值是零\N{\fs38}just went from being worth one of itself to zero of itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.10,0:18:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点 同志们\N{\fs38}-Dear God, no. -Calm down, people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启用银河联邦自卫队 颁布戒严令\N{\fs38}Deploy the Galactic militia and declare martial law.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官 遵命\N{\fs38}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我们用什么付他们工资啊\N{\fs38}Uh, what should I pay them with?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.90,0:18:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为国家效劳的荣耀就是他们的报酬\N{\fs38}Their payment is the honor they’ll feel to serve their --
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 我凭啥对他大喊大叫 谁付我钱啊\N{\fs38}Wait. Who’s paying me to yell at this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能回答 如果给我钱的话\N{\fs38}I can answer that -- for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没想到我还能看到这么一幕\N{\fs38}I never thought I’d live to see this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同志们 同志们 别吵了\N{\fs38}Gentlemen! Gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实还有个你们没想到的方法\N{\fs38}There’s a solution here you’re not seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 把你的夹克给我 - 快把裤子扒下来给我\N{\fs38}-Give me your jacket! -Give me those pants!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.86,0:18:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在没有贫富之分了\N{\fs38}Insectoid Employee: There's no rich people or poor people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要更多夹克\N{\fs38}I want more jackets!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得最多裤子者得天下\N{\fs38}He who controls the pants controls the galaxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.57,0:19:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决不给虫子再次统治地表世界的机会\N{\fs38}No longer will the insects have domain over surface world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 到底发生什么了啊\N{\fs38}Jerry, what the hell is happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银河联邦垮台了\N{\fs38}The Galactic government collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fs38}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 虽然说出来并不光彩 但是\N{\fs38}Look.I’m not proud to share this, but the truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才一路爬回来的 这招真管用\N{\fs38}I just kept crawling, and it kept working.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事就太好了\N{\fs38}-[ Exhales deeply] -Oh, I’m glad you’re okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.68,0:19:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直纵容你爸爸 是不是就要一直为此付出代价\N{\fs38}Are we ever going to sTop paying for indulging your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经失去了孩子 地球 和工作\N{\fs38}Our children, our planet, our jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.39,0:19:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们还拥有什么呢\N{\fs38}Is there anything left to lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩彼此了 而且我永远不会离开你的\N{\fs38}Just each other, and I’ll never let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起我做了这些事\N{\fs38}And I’m so sorry I ever did this to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.94,0:19:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜猜是谁把政府搞垮了\N{\fs38}Guess who dismantled the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.28,0:19:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 求求你别再离开我了 - 再也不会了 宝贝\N{\fs38}-Please don’t leave me again. -l never will, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是对的 他是故意自首的\N{\fs38}I was right! He turned himself in on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在他的计划之中\N{\fs38}It was all part of his plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.87,0:19:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 还有淡啤酒吗\N{\fs38}Jerry, is there any light beer left?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本想不到你在监狱里会想念什么\N{\fs38}It’s insane what you miss in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 没有\N{\fs38}Urn, okay. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不 没有 很明确地告诉你\N{\fs38}No, no, no. Foot-down tirne.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 你是对的 有伏特加吗\N{\fs38}No. You’re right. Where’s the vodka?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Beth你来选吧 有他没我 有我没他\N{\fs38}Beth, it’s him or me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来你们需要单独谈谈\N{\fs38}Seems like you guys need some privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我还是去车库吧\N{\fs38}Ill, uh, I’ll be in the garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么啊 Jerry\N{\fs38}What the fuck?! Not cool, Jerry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车库是男人的城堡\N{\fs38}A man’s garage is his castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry会花一些时间回归单身了\N{\fs38}Jerry’s going to spend some time.. .divorced.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 那太遗憾了 宝贝\N{\fs38}Oh. Oh, I-I’m sorry to hear that, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个决定不是因为我吧\N{\fs38}I hope I had nothing to do with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 天啊 爸爸 别想太多 和你没什么关系\N{\fs38}Oh, God. Dad, that is not your burden to bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉很内疚 把你想得这么坏\N{\fs38}I feel terrible that I misjudged you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样对Jerry也好\N{\fs38}This is gonna be good for Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 对所有人都好 - 对所有人都好\N{\fs38}-For everybody. -For everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.67,0:20:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最好去看看他\N{\fs38}-[ Celiphone whooshes] -I better tend to Jerry
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以免他改变主意 不想搬出去了\N{\fs38}before he changes his mind and doesn’t move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.55,0:20:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不打扰你们两个的小冒险了\N{\fs38}I will leave you two to your adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天爷\N{\fs38}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nancy说他们正在学校操场里对那些外星人用刑\N{\fs38}Nancy says they’re drawing and quartering aliens in the school courtyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这算是爱国行为\N{\fs38}and it technically counts as patriotism.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.31,0:21:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 我的父母真的要离婚吗\N{\fs38}Geez! Are my parents seriously gonna get divorced?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.27,0:21:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 Rick 我要去\N{\fs38}All right, Rick. I’m gonna go to my -- Gah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪也别去 Morty 你听见你妈妈说的了\N{\fs38}Not so fast, Morty. You heard your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还要去一起冒险呢 Morty 就你和我\N{\fs38}We’ve got adventures to go on, Morty, just you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时带上你姐姐 或者你妈妈\N{\fs38}And sometimes your sister and sometimes your mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.15,0:21:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但绝不带你爸爸\N{\fs38}but never your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想知道原因吗 Morty 因为他惹恼我了\N{\fs38}You want to know why, Morty? Because he crossed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.32,0:21:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等会儿 Rick 这有点黑暗\N{\fs38}Okay. Take it easy, Rick. T-That's dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 还会更黑暗的 Morty\N{\fs38}Oh, it gets darker, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到冒险中最黑暗的时刻\N{\fs38}Welcome to the darkest year of our adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 第一个改变 你爸爸出局了 - 哦 天啊\N{\fs38}- First thing that’s different ---no more Dad, Morty. -Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他威胁说要把我交给政府\N{\fs38}He threatened to turn me in to the government,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,0:21:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我设计让他和政府都滚蛋了\N{\fs38}so I made him and the government go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs38}Oh, fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政府还有他现在都被我取代了\N{\fs38}I’ve rep[burps]Iaced them both as the de facto patriarch
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你家和这个宇宙都是我做主\N{\fs38}of your family and your universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 如果我不带着你和你姐姐回家 - 哦天\N{\fs38}Your mom wouldn’t have accepted me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈就不会接受我\N{\fs38}if I came home without you and your sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.84,0:21:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 所以你现在知道我救你们的真正原因了 - 噢\N{\fs38}so now you know the real reason I rescued you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.76,0:21:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚刚掌控了整个家 Morty\N{\fs38}I just took over the family, Morty,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你向你妈妈或者你姐姐告密\N{\fs38}and if you tell your mom or sister I said any of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.01,0:21:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不承认 他们会相信我 因为我是英雄 Morty\N{\fs38}I’ll deny it, and they’ll take my side,because I’m a hero, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.77,0:21:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你不得不乖乖按我说的做了 Morty 永远\N{\fs38}Now you’re gonna have to go and do whatever I say, Morty,Forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.81,0:21:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我要出去 再找点那个\N{\fs38}And I'll -- I'll go out and I'll find some more of that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.69,0:21:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了<花木兰>电影推出的川香酱了 Morty\N{\fs38}“Mulan” Szechuan teriyaki dipping sauce, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊\N{\fs38}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一切都是为了川香酱 Morty\N{\fs38}Because that’s --that’s what this is all about, Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 川香 - 那才是一切背后的动力\N{\fs38}-Szechuan? -That’s my one-armed man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.82,0:21:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是为了给死去的妻女复仇 Morty\N{\fs38}I’m not driven by avenging my dead family, Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.78,0:21:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是假的\N{\fs38}That was fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.78,0:21:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是为了麦乐鸡的蘸酱\N{\fs38}I-I’m driven by finding that McNugget sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:21:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 麦乐鸡 - 我要吃那个<花木兰>的麦乐鸡蘸酱 Morty\N{\fs38}I want that “Mulan” McNugget sauce, Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.62,0:22:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这才是串起一切的主线 Morty - 你在胡说什么\N{\fs38}-That’s my series arc, Morty! -What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.33,0:22:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这个要拍九季 我一定要找到这个麦乐鸡蘸酱\N{\fs38}If it takes nine seasons, I want my McNugget dipping sauce --
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.54,0:22:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 川香酱 Morty - 你到底在胡言乱语些什么\N{\fs38}-Szechuan sauce, Morty. -What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.50,0:22:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个蘸酱会一路让我们走到最后\N{\fs38}That’s what’s gonna take us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.54,0:22:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Morty - 你在说什么啊\N{\fs38}-all the way to the end, Morty. -What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.59,0:22:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有九季 Morty\N{\fs38}Nine more seasons, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要九季 直到我找到川香酱\N{\fs38}Nine more seasons until I get that dipping Szechuan sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.38,0:22:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那是什么啊 - 也就是还要97年 Morty\N{\fs38}-What is that?! -For 97 more years, Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.13,0:22:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊到底\N{\fs38}What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.13,0:22:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说我要那个麦乐鸡的蘸酱 Morty\N{\fs38}I want that McNugget sauce, Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.42,0:22:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了吗\N{\fs38}Is it ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.42,0:22:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 现在就可以让它上线\N{\fs38}Yes. We can bring it online now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:22:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fs38}Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.80,0:23:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是凤凰人\N{\fs38}I am Phoenix Person.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.77,0:23:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凤凰人 这是我们决定好的名字吗\N{\fs38}Phoenix Person? Is that what we settled on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.43,0:23:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为我们说好的是赛博鸟\N{\fs38}I thought we all agreed on Cyber Bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你不在意他叫什么名字的\N{\fs38}Y-You said you didn’t care what he was called
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.40,0:23:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我们把他救回来就行\N{\fs38}as long as we brought him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.81,0:23:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这么说的 但是凤凰人也太不像话了吧\N{\fs38}Yeah, but Phoenix Person?
